{
  "texts": [
    "Policies that promote the inclusion of diverse perspectives in AI development can help ensure that AI systems are equitable and beneficial to all segments of society.",
    "Additionally, the establishment of independent bodies to oversee AI ethics and compliance can provide an additional layer of oversight, ensuring that AI technologies adhere to ethical standards.",
    "The study highlights the need for international collaboration in developing policies and regulations that address the global nature of AI technology and its impacts.",
    "Encouraging the adoption of ethical AI standards across industries can foster a culture of responsibility and ethics in AI development.",
    "Ultimately, effective policy and regulation are essential for harnessing the potential of AI technologies while safeguarding against biases and ensuring fairness for all."
  ]
}